ParamsInitializer<MPPInitParams>, CompatibleWithMark
public class KernelBirthPartition
extends KernelBirth<MarksFromPartition>
Proposes new marks ONLY if they haven't already been proposed and accepted.

As an example, this is like sampling WITHOUT replacement.

Author:
Owen Feehan
